headline: Is Public Storage (PSA) Offering Value After Recent Share Price Strength?
summary: If you are wondering whether Public Storage is priced fairly at around US$300.35, it helps to step back and look at what the current share price might be implying about the business. The stock has recent returns of 4.7% over 7 days, 2.2% over 30 days, 16.2% year to date, 5.2% over 1 year and 13.6% and 58.6% over 3 and 5 years respectively, which can shape how the market is currently thinking about its growth prospects and risk.
